snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator VR - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Discover your cleaning style in PowerWash Simulator VR, the upcoming virtual reality version of the hit cleaning simulator game. Use a variety of power washer attachments and soaps on Meta Quest when the game arrives in 2023.
